  <title translate="true">CNC: GWT Constant Concentration Package Pane</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">CNC: GWT Constant Concentration Package Pane</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">CNC: GWT Constant Concentration Package</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> pane is on the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MODFLOW_Features_Tab" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">MODFLOW Features</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> tab of the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Object_Properties_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Object Properties</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The data that can be specified for the CNC package are the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Starting time</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Ending time</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, and </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Specified concentration</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> and the </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Chemical Species</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">. The </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Specified concentration</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> is the specified concentration at the selected cells for the selected </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Chemical Species</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Specified Concentration Active is used to activate or deactivate</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> &quot;</text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Specified Concentration Active</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">&quot; can be used to turn on or off a CNC boundary. If the formula for </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Specified Concentration Active</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> evaluates to True, a specified concentration boundary will be defined. If it evaluates to False, a specified concentration boundary will not be defined. This can be used to turn on or off specified concentration boundaries at different locations based on a criterion specified by the user. Such a capability can be useful for specifying tidal boundaries where some locations may be alternately flooded or exposed.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Specified Concentration</text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true"> Multiplier</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> is only used if it has been activated in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="CNC-GWT-Constant-Concentration" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">CNC: GWT Constant Concentration Package Pane</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">. If </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Specified Concentration</text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true"> Multiplier</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> is specified, the concentration is multiplied by the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Specified Concentration</text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true"> Multiplier</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> value.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Starting time</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Ending time</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> are explained in the help for the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MODFLOW_Features_Tab" anchor="Times" styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">MODFLOW Features</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> tab.</text></para>
  </body>
